    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has plenty of life left for all your weekend adventures or daily commutes. I\u2019ve taken great care of it, and it runs like a charm! If you\u2019re looking for something reliable and ready to hit the road today, this is the one for you. It's been super dependable for me, and I know you'll love it too. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 32500.0,
