      "description": "We are pleased to present this exceptionally well-maintained vehicle, an exemplary specimen that balances sophisticated performance with long-term reliability. This automobile has undergone a comprehensive professional assessment to ensure mechanical excellence and structural integrity. The interior cabin remains refined, and the exterior reflects a history of diligent care. For the discerning driver seeking a robust and prestigious transport solution, this vehicle represents a premier investment in quality and automotive engineering.",
      "price": 36500.0,
