      "description": "This E92 M3 is powered by the high-revving S65 4.0L V8, featuring eight independent throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system. The 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile engagement, paired with a GKN-sourced variable M differential for optimal power delivery. The suspension geometry utilizes aluminum subframes and EDC-adjustable damping to maintain a balanced roll center. Preventative maintenance is up to date, including rod bearing shells and throttle actuators, ensuring the valvetrain and reciprocating assembly are track-ready. A true driver's car with a linear power curve and a visceral 8,400 RPM redline.",
